OL,5, Long-serving Guardian cartoonist Steve 
OL,6, Bell has been sacked by the newspaper  
OL,7, in a row over a drawing he created of  
OL,8, Israeli leader Benjamin Netanyahu.     
OL,10,FThe cartoon, featuring Netanyahu       
OL,11,Foperating on his own stomach, showed a 
OL,12,Fcut in the outline of the Gaza Strip.  
OL,14,FBell said the cartoon was spiked after 
OL,15,Fa phone call from the paper suggested  
OL,16,Fit may reference Shakespeare's         
OL,17,FShylock's "pound of flesh" line.       
OL,19,FHe said it was inspired by a 60s       
OL,20,Fcartoon of President Lyndon B Johnson. 
